      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under formal version control with documented release notes and regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under institutional license with documented version control, release notes, and a regression test suite. All relevant hemolysis flow regime tests pass. Required level 2 achieved."
