      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate convergence to analytic or manufactured solutions for rotating-frame Navier-Stokes at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Verification against Taylor-Couette and lid-driven cavity manufactured solutions confirms second-order spatial accuracy. Rotating-frame MRF implementation verified against published benchmarks. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
