      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for the primary QoI (hemolysis index) across at least three mesh refinement levels with GCI < 5%.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (3.2M, 8.7M, 22.1M cells). GCI for normalised hemolysis index is 3.1% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
