      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must match the COU operating envelope (flow rate 2–8 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM) within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments span 2–8 L/min and 2000–3500 RPM with calibrated flow meters (±1%) and tachometers (±0.5%). Conditions overlap fully with CPB COU envelope. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
