      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within ±15% across all 5 validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted normalised hemolysis index agrees with FDA experimental data within 8–12% across all 5 operating points. Systematic bias is less than 5%. Acceptance criterion met. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
