      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs computed by the model (hemolysis index, wall shear stress distribution) must directly map to the clinical decision metric (relative hemolysis index RH).",
      "rationale": "The primary model output is the power-law hemolysis index (HI), which is directly transformed to the relative hemolysis index RH used in the regulatory acceptance criterion. The mapping is analytically defined and documented. Required level 2 achieved."
