    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD hemolysis predictions agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within 12% across all 5 operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device. The package is submitted under the Minimal profile with hash integrity protection; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be affixed prior to regulatory submission.",
